因此本庭赦免你的死刑
I hereby commute your sentence,

70
00:06:08,360 --> 00:06:11,030
宣判你将被处以徒刑
and order that you be imprisoned for the remainder

71
00:06:11,170 --> 00:06:14,030
在监狱里度过你那行尸走肉般的悲惨余生
of your miserable, moribund, mutton-chopped life.

72
00:06:14,170 --> 00:06:16,100
-什么  -吊死他
- What?! - Hang him!

73
00:06:16,240 --> 00:06:17,430
-吊死他  -闭庭
- Hang him! - There.

74
00:06:18,170 --> 00:06:20,940
-胡说八道  -吊死他  把他吊起来
- Balderdash! - String him up! Hang him high!

75
00:06:22,580 --> 00:06:25,240
法庭将安排将囚犯押至
Means shall be arranged to transport this prisoner

76
00:06:25,380 --> 00:06:27,410
伦敦塔
to the Tower of London.

77
00:06:38,790 --> 00:06:40,230
非常感谢
Thanks very much.

78
00:06:44,600 --> 00:06:45,790
拜拜
Ta.

79
00:06:49,600 --> 00:06:52,230
快点  给我上去
Come on. Get up there.

80
00:06:54,610 --> 00:06:56,370
上去
Get up!

81
00:07:01,050 --> 00:07:04,710
真见鬼  这下咱们俩都得进去了
Hell's teeth. Now we're both headed for prison.

82
00:07:04,820 --> 00:07:07,520
别担心  我买通了车夫
Not to worry. I've paid off the driver.

83
00:07:07,690 --> 00:07:11,060
用不了十分钟  咱们就出了伦敦城  有马等着
Ten minutes, we'll be outside London Town, horses waiting.

84
00:07:11,160 --> 00:07:12,720
今晚  我们就能到海边
Tonight, we make the coast.

85
00:07:12,830 --> 00:07:15,190
再然后就是弄艘船的问题了
Then it's just a matter of finding a ship.

86
00:07:16,460 --> 00:07:19,130
-这都计划好了吗  -没错
- All part of the plan, yes? - Exactly.

87
00:07:19,270 --> 00:07:21,200
我今早刚到伦敦城
I arrived in London Town just this morning

88
00:07:21,370 --> 00:07:22,410
来救和绞刑架有个约会的
to rescue one Joshamee

89
00:07:22,410 --> 00:07:24,500
名叫约什米・吉布斯的家伙
Gibbs from one appointment with the gallows.

90
00:07:24,640 --> 00:07:26,440
鉴于你目前还活得好好的
Seeing as how you're still alive,

91
00:07:26,570 --> 00:07:29,300
我认为目前为止还挺成功
I'd say it's all been very successful thus far.

92
00:07:29,980 --> 00:07:31,170
你怎么了  吉布斯
What happened to you, Gibbs?

93
00:07:31,310 --> 00:07:33,870
我以为你出海了或是在忙别的
I thought you were employed elsewhere or otherwise engaged.

94
00:07:34,050 --> 00:07:35,390
没错  可我一直在
Aye. But I always listened

95
00:07:35,390 --> 00:07:37,510
打探黑珍珠号的消息
like a thief for news of the Black Pearl.

96
00:07:37,650 --> 00:07:40,120
谁也不知道她会停靠在何处
Nobody's seen where she might next make port.

97
00:07:40,250 --> 00:07:42,310
后来  我听到流言
Then, I hear a rumor:

98
00:07:42,460 --> 00:07:45,950
杰克・史派罗在伦敦找了条船  在招募水手
Jack Sparrow's in London with a ship and looking for a crew.

99
00:07:46,090 --> 00:07:47,820
-才怪  -可我是这么听说
- Am not. - But that's what I heard.

100
00:07:47,960 --> 00:07:50,190
说你今晚就在
Fact is, you're signing up men tonight.

101
00:07:50,330 --> 00:07:51,860
"船长之女"酒吧招人
Pub called The Captain's Daughter.

102
00:07:52,000 --> 00:07:55,230
-才怪  -我是觉得有点奇怪
- Am not! - Well, I thought it a bit odd,

103
00:07:55,400 --> 00:07:59,100
不过话说回来  你做事总是这么不靠谱
but then, you've never been the most predictable of sorts.

104
00:07:59,970 --> 00:08:01,240
跟我好好说说
Tell me something.

105
00:08:01,410 --> 00:08:04,900
这儿还有个叫杰克・史派罗的家伙冒充我的大名
There is another Jack Sparrow out there sullying my good name?

106
00:08:05,080 --> 00:08:07,210
-冒名的骗子  -没错
- An impostor. - Indeed.

107
00:08:07,350 --> 00:08:11,110
不过  人家有船
But... an impostor with a ship.

108
00:08:11,220 --> 00:08:13,810
还有水手
And in need of a crew.

109
00:08:13,960 --> 00:08:15,980
这些  苍天在上  我也会有
Which, as fate would have it, so am I.

110
00:08:16,990 --> 00:08:18,580
你怎么样  杰克
What about you, Jack?

111
00:08:18,760 --> 00:08:22,590
我上回听说  你拼了老命要找那不老泉
Last I heard, you were hell-bent to find the Fountain of Youth.

112
00:08:22,760 --> 00:08:24,250
运气如何
Any luck?

113
00:08:26,330 --> 00:08:29,270
经历了千辛万苦后  我顿悟了
Circumstances arose and forced a compelling insight

114
00:08:29,440 --> 00:08:31,410
此行既需要勇气  也得小心谨慎
regarding discretion and valor.

115
00:08:31,540 --> 00:08:34,670
-那就是说  你放弃了  -我没有
- Meaning, you gave up. - I did not.

116
00:08:34,810 --> 00:08:37,610
我还是一样不要命  妥妥的
I am just as bent as ever. Hellishly so.

117
00:08:37,780 --> 00:08:42,580
我一定要尝尝那泉水  吉布斯水手长  我把话撂在这儿
I shall taste those waters, Master Gibbs. Mark my words.

118
