你好像漏了"船长"二字
There should be a "Captain" In there somewhere.

123
00:10:36,930 --> 00:10:39,460
我听过你
I've heard of you.

124
00:10:39,600 --> 00:10:41,660
你一定知道我是谁
And you know who I am.

125
00:10:42,670 --> 00:10:45,260
看起来挺面熟  我是不是恐吓过你
Face is familiar. Have I threatened you before?

126
00:10:45,370 --> 00:10:47,710
在你面前的是乔治・奥古斯都
You are in the presence of George Augustus,

127
