黑胡子干的  管事儿的都是
Blackbeard's doing. All the officers are the same.

364
00:31:44,030 --> 00:31:45,760
这样的人更服从命令
Makes 'em more compliant.

365
00:31:47,030 --> 00:31:49,000
还有没完没了的坏脾气
And perpetually ill-tempered.

366
00:31:50,700 --> 00:31:53,300
-快擦  -好
- Come on. Scrub.  - Yeah.

367
00:32:00,380 --> 00:32:04,010
拉  拉  拉
Pull! Pull! Pull!

368
