船长  我想举报一场叛乱
Captain, I wish to report a mutiny.

509
00:44:32,500 --> 00:44:34,090
我能指名道姓
I can name fingers and point names.

510
00:44:34,270 --> 00:44:35,730
不需要  史派罗先生
No need, Mr. Sparrow.

511
00:44:35,870 --> 00:44:39,100
他们是羊群  而你  是牧羊人
They are sheep. You, their shepherd.

512
00:44:44,010 --> 00:44:46,710
我有说过吗  船长  你女儿是个美女
Have I mentioned, sir, what a lovely daughter you have?

513
00:44:47,350 --> 00:44:49,780
你小子死前还挺有眼福
A fitting last sight for a doomed soul.

514
00:44:49,950 --> 00:44:52,350
等等  父亲  我们需要他
Remember, Father. We need him.

515
00:44:52,480 --> 00:44:53,970
如果我不时常杀个人
If I don't kill a man every now and then,

516
00:44:54,090 --> 00:44:56,520
-他们会忘了我是谁  -懦夫
- they forget who I am.  - Coward!

517
00:44:58,160 --> 00:45:00,390
他们不会忘
They do not forget.

518
